name: R5-ClaimResponse-R4-ClaimResponse
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R5 ClaimResponse into FHIR R4

element.display: Response to a claim predetermination or preauthorization

target.display: Response to a claim predetermination or preauthorization
target.comment: R5 `ClaimResponse` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ClaimResponse`
R5 `ClaimResponse.addItem` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ClaimResponse.addItem`

R5 `ClaimResponse.addItem.adjudication` maps as RelatedTo to R4 `ClaimResponse.addItem.adjudication` - adjudication made the element mandatory; adjudication increased the minimum cardinality from 0 to 1

R5 `ClaimResponse.addItem.bodySite` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4 `ClaimResponse.addItem.bodySite` - bodySite changed from array to scalar (max cardinality from * to 1); bodySite added a binding requirement - Example http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/tooth; bodySite has change due to type change: R5 bodySite BackboneElement has no equivalent or mapped type in R4 bodySite
